                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Effortless Expansion: Cast \"Effortless Expansion\" and lower the cap to the next level about 20% in the next 5 days. (Cooldown 20 days)",
                    "target": "轻松扩展：施放“轻松扩展”，在接下来的 5 天内将升至下一级的上限降低约 20%。（冷却 20 天）"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Recursive Reflection: Improve your notes and get 5 times the points you get on normal condition for the next 5 hours. Cooldown 3 days.",
                    "target": "递归反思：接下来的 5 小时内改进笔记可获得正常条件下 5 倍积分。冷却 3 天。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
