                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Serenity achieved! As a 'Zen Knowledge Keeper,' you maintain a tranquil mind while managing vast pools of knowledge with grace and poise.",
                    "target": "宁静已达成！作为“禅意知识守护者”，你在管理浩瀚知识池的同时，依然保持内心平和、从容优雅。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "All hail the 'Grand Archivist Overlord!' You wield the knowledge of ages and hold the keys to unlock the gates of wisdom!",
                    "target": "向“档案大总管”致敬！你掌握千古智慧，并持有开启智慧之门的钥匙！"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Congratulations, oh wise one! You've attained the highest level of enlightenment as the 'Omniscient Sage of Everything.' Your understanding knows no bounds, and your wisdom is as vast as the cosmos itself!",
                    "target": "恭喜你，睿智之人！你已达到最高境界，成为“全知万物的智者”。你的理解无边无际，你的智慧如同宇宙般浩瀚！"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Welcome to the journey of knowledge! As a 'Lore Seeker Initiate,' you've taken your first steps into the world of organized wisdom. Your quest has just begun, and with each note you make, you lay the foundation for a future rich with insights and understanding. Your journey starts here, and the path ahead is filled with potential and discovery.",
                    "target": "欢迎踏上知识之旅！作为“传说探寻者·入门者”，你已迈出通往有序智慧世界的第一步。你的探索刚刚开始，每一条笔记都在为充满洞见与理解的未来奠基。你的旅程从这里启航，前方之路充满潜力与发现。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "You've hit the ground running with your existing knowledge treasures! You're already an 'Lore Apprentice,' armed with a wealth of wisdom and ready to shape it further.",
                    "target": "凭借现有的知识宝藏，你一出发就已疾驰！你已经是“传说学徒”，手握丰富智慧，准备继续锤炼它。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Your existing notes have given you a head start! You're now a 'Savvy Scholar,' confidently diving into the sea of information with a treasure trove of insights.",
                    "target": "你的现有笔记让你先人一步！你现在是“精明学者”，带着满满的洞见宝库，自信地潜入信息之海。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Building upon your pre-existing notes, you're establishing the 'Sage's Foundation' for an even grander edifice of knowledge. Your groundwork is impressive!",
                    "target": "在既有笔记之上，你正在建立“智者之基”，为更宏伟的知识殿堂打下基础。你的底蕴令人赞叹！"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Your existing notes have nurtured the growth of a 'Wisdom Seedling.' You're cultivating your garden of knowledge with care and patience.",
                    "target": "你的现有笔记滋养了“智慧幼苗”的成长。你正以细心与耐心培育你的知识花园。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Thanks to your prior efforts, you're a 'Prodigious Preparer,' standing tall among your notes and ready to conquer new realms of understanding.",
                    "target": "得益于你此前的努力，你成为“卓越筹备者”，在笔记中挺立，准备征服新的理解疆域。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Your past notes have led you to the grand 'Epic Epiphany Explorer' status! You've already been down a few rabbit holes and come out with dazzling discoveries.",
                    "target": "你的过往笔记让你跻身“史诗顿悟探险家”的崇高之境！你已经钻过不少“兔子洞”，带回令人目眩的发现。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "With your existing notes illuminating your path, you've become a 'Lore Luminary,' shining light on the mysteries of the universe, one idea at a time.",
                    "target": "在现有笔记照亮道路的指引下，你已成为“传说之光”，一次一个想法，照亮宇宙的奥秘。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Armed with your existing notes, you're the 'Eureka Maestro,' composing a symphony of insights that harmonize with the melody of discovery.",
                    "target": "有了现有笔记作伴，你就是“尤里卡大师”，谱写与发现旋律相和的洞见交响曲。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "With your existing notes standing as a testament, you've ascended to the illustrious 'Chronicles Champion' level. Your journey through time's tapestry has brought forth a symphony of insights that harmonize past and present.",
                    "target": "凭借你已有的笔记作为见证，你已晋升至卓越的“编年史冠军”级别。你穿梭于时间织锦的旅程，奏响了洞见的交响曲，使过去与现在和谐共鸣。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "As 'The Curious Cartographer,' your existing notes have mapped out uncharted territories of understanding. Your curiosity knows no bounds, and your notes are the compass guiding your exploration.",
                    "target": "作为“好奇的制图师”，你现有的笔记绘制出了未被探索的理解疆域。你的好奇心没有边界，而你的笔记就是引导探索的罗盘。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Your existing notes have made you the 'Sultan of Synthesis.' You're the master weaver, threading together threads of information into a rich tapestry of insight.",
                    "target": "你现有的笔记让你成为“综合苏丹”。你是编织大师，将信息的丝线交织成丰厚的洞见织锦。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "At the pinnacle of personal knowledge mastery, you're now revered as the 'Eternal Archivist.' Your existing notes, carefully curated and nurtured, stand as immortal beacons, guiding seekers through the labyrinth of knowledge across ages.",
                    "target": "在个人知识掌握的巅峰，你如今被尊称为“永恒档案师”。你精心整理与培育的既有笔记如不朽灯塔般矗立，指引求知者穿越历代的知识迷宫。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Congratulations! You've woven a tapestry of knowledge for 30 consecutive days. As a 'Consistent Lore Weaver,' your daily contributions have become the threads that enrich the fabric of your growing wisdom.",
                    "target": "恭喜！你连续30天编织了知识的织锦。作为“持续传说编织者”，你的每日贡献已成为丰富你不断增长智慧纹理的丝线。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "You've forged a robust foundation with 90 consecutive days of dedicated note crafting. As a 'Knowledge Artisan Stalwart,' your commitment has sculpted your repository into a work of art, a testament to your persistent curiosity.",
                    "target": "你以连续90天的专注笔记打造出坚实的基础。作为“知识工匠坚守者”，你的投入将你的知识库雕琢成艺术之作，见证你持久的好奇心。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "With each passing day, you've laid down the blueprints of a profound structure. As a 'Wisdom Architect Virtuoso' at 180 days, your continuous efforts have transformed your knowledge space into an architectural marvel, a testament to your enduring passion for learning.",
                    "target": "日复一日，你铺就了一座深邃结构的蓝图。到第180天，作为“智慧建筑师大师”，你的持续努力已将知识空间化为建筑奇观，见证你对学习的恒久热情。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "A year of unwavering dedication! You've earned the title of 'Eternal Scholar Maestro' by contributing daily for 365 days. Your commitment has created a masterpiece of continuous learning, setting you apart as a true maestro of personal knowledge.",
                    "target": "一年如一日的坚定投入！你通过连续365天每日贡献，赢得了“永恒学者大师”的称号。你的承诺铸就了持续学习的杰作，使你成为真正的个人知识大师。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "description",
                    "source": "Precision Prism: 4 times the points when increasing the \"note length maturity\" for a note the next 3 hours.",
                    "target": "精准棱镜：在接下来的3小时内提升笔记的“长度成熟度”时，积分获得4倍。"
